config BR2_PACKAGE_RASPUTIN_API
	bool "rasputin-api"
	default y
	help
	  The Rasputin control-plane backend. Embeds NATS+JetStream, hosts
	  the SQLite job/inventory/auth stores, serves the web UI + REST/WS
	  API, and orchestrates the saga job runner.

	  Ships on EVERY Rasputin OS image but its systemd unit only starts
	  on the controlplane role (ConditionEnvironment=RASPUTIN_NODE_ROLE=
	  controlplane). See os-images/provisioning.md §2.

	  Installed from a pre-built release binary — see
	  package/rasputin-api/rasputin-api.mk.
